  open() { /* slide in and render current state */ },
  close() { /* slide out */ },
  toggle() { /* open if closed, close if open */ },
  render(state) { /* render full state */ },
  highlightChange(changedKeys) { /* optional: emphasize changed flags */ }
};

export default EmotionalDrawer;
```

---

## 9. Performance & Accessibility

- Ensure smooth animation at 60fps on mid‑range devices.
- Use ARIA roles:
  - `role="complementary"` or `role="dialog"` depending on implementation.
- Provide text labels for all icons.
- Maintain sufficient color contrast for all text and meters.

---

## 10. Future Extensions

- Aspect‑based background themes.
- Audio cues tied to major metaphysical shifts.
- Historical mini‑graph of one or more flags.
- Integration with achievement or title systems.
